Trello,is,an,online,project,management,and,collaboration,platform,Users,can,manage,their,projects,on,Trello,boards,that,display,the,various,aspects,of,their,projects,such,as,what,has,been,done,and,who,is,working,on,what,The,Trello,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,data,and,functionality,of,Trello,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,project,information,managing,user,information,and,viewing,lists,and,tasks